overview.en: M mall is a pioneer of the new generation of social e-commerce and a practitioner of the real sharing economy. M mall will fully implement the certification economy system and let consumers, distributors and suppliers become the main owners of the value of the platform.
overview.zh: M商城是新一代社交电商的引领者，是真正的共享经济的践行者，M商城将全面践行通证经济制度，让消费者、分享者、供应商成为平台价值的主要拥有者。
